widget", "widgetType": "heading", "settings": {"title": "Booking software, made with a boutique's eye.", "header_size": "h1", "align": "left", "title_color": "#2E332B", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Cormorant Garamond", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 54, "sizes": []}, "typography_font_weight": "500", "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.12, "sizes": []}, "_margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "10", "left": "0", "isLinked": false}}, "elements": []}, {"id": "31ece13", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "divider", "settings": {"color": "#A78C46", "weight": {"unit": "px", "size": 1, "sizes": []}, "width": {"unit": "px", "size": 64, "sizes": []}, "align": "left", "gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 18, "sizes": []}, "_margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "16", "right": "0", "bottom": "16", "left": "0", "isLinked": false}}, "elements": []}, {"id": "424bfa9", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": {"editor": "<p>Ivory Digital is a Manchester-based studio dedicated to one thing: giving bridal boutiques beautiful, dependable booking software they actually own.</p>", "align": "left", "text_color": "#3C4237", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Jost", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 18, "sizes": []}, "typography_font_weight": "400", "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.7, "sizes": []}}, "elements": []}], "isInner": true}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "5f5f4f6", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "flex_direction": "column", "flex_align_items": "center", "background_background": "classic", "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "78", "right": "20", "bottom": "78", "left": "20", "isLinked": false}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "background_color": "#ffffff"}, "elements": [{"id": "ae12599", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "boxed", "flex_direction": "column", "flex_align_items": "flex-start", "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": false}}, "elements": [{"id": "8e995f3", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": {"editor": "<p>Bridal is a business of first impressions and precious moments. Yet so many boutiques still juggle a paper diary, missed calls during fittings, and clunky third-party booking widgets that look nothing like their brand \u2014 and quietly charge a fee on every booking.</p>", "align": "left", "text_color": "#79806E", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Jost", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 16, "sizes": []}, "typography_font_weight": "400", "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.7, "sizes": []}}, "elements": []}, {"id": "55909f0", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": {"editor": "<p>We built Ivory Digital to change that. We create a private, elegant booking system for each boutique: a customer-facing website that feels like a natural extension of your shop, paired with a powerful behind-the-scenes diary that keeps your team calm and in control. No generic widget, no per-booking commission \u2014 just software that works the way you do.</p>", "align": "left", "text_color": "#79806E", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Jost", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 16, "sizes": []}, "typography_font_weight": "400", "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.7, "sizes": []}}, "elements": []}, {"id": "ce3781f", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "heading", "settings": {"title": "How we work", "header_size": "h2", "align": "left", "title_color": "#2E332B", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Cormorant Garamond", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 40, "sizes": []}, "typography_font_weight": "500", "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.12, "sizes": []}, "_margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "10", "left": "0", "isLinked": false}}, "elements": []}, {"id": "9b3eb92", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "divider", "settings": {"color": "#A78C46", "weight": {"unit": "px", "size": 1, "sizes": []}, "width": {"unit": "px", "size": 64, "sizes": []}, "align": "left", "gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 18, "sizes": []}, "_margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "16", "right": "0", "bottom": "16", "left": "0", "isLinked": false}}, "elements": []}, {"id": "3f254bf", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": {"editor": "<p>Every system is bespoke. We learn how your boutique runs \u2014 your appointment types, your questions, your hours and how many brides you can see at once \u2014 and shape the software around it. Then we brand it to you, host it on your domain, and look after it with a simple maintenance package so you can focus on your brides.</p>", "align": "left", "text_color": "#79806E", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_family": "Jost", "typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 16, "sizes": []}, "typography_font_weight": "400", "typography_line_height": {"unit": "em", "size": 1.7, "sizes": []}}, "elements": []}], "isInner": true}, {"id": "02452a4", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "boxed", "flex_direction": "row", "flex_wrap": "wrap", "flex_justify_content": "flex-start", "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 26, "sizes": [], "column": "26", "row": "26"}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": false}}, "elements": [{"id": "c67fe5e", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "flex_direction": "column", "background_background": "classic", "background_color": "#ffffff", "border_border": "solid", "border_width": {"unit": "px", "top": "1", "right": "1", "bottom": "1", "left": "1", "isLinked": false}, "border_color": "#DEE